[[File:Explosiveblaster.jpg|thumb|Explosive blaster pistol]]
The '''explosive blaster pistol''' was very similar to the standard [[Blaster pistol/Legends|blaster pistol]]. But their shots would explode upon impact and deal moderate to devastating damage to any combatant who was hit by them. These shots were similar to shots from a [[Particle cannon turret|particle cannon]].

